SELECT 
    'ChangePayableItem' || '::' || "PayableItem_Changes"."ID"  AS "ID",
    "PayableItem"."ID"                                         AS "PayableItem",
    "PayableItem_Changes"."Time"                               AS "Time",
    "PayableItem_Changes"."ChangedBy"                          AS "ExecutedBy",
    "PayableItem_Changes"."Attribute"                          AS "ChangedAttribute",
    "PayableItem_Changes"."ExecutionType"                      AS "ExecutionType",
    "PayableItem_Changes"."OldValue"                           AS "OldValue",
    "PayableItem_Changes"."NewValue"                           AS "NewValue"
FROM "o_custom_PayableItem" AS "PayableItem"
    LEFT JOIN "c_o_custom_PayableItem" AS "PayableItem_Changes"
        ON "PayableItem"."ID" = "PayableItem_Changes"."ObjectID"
WHERE "PayableItem_Changes"."Attribute" NOT IN ('Clearing','Payment', 'ReversalPayment', 'ReversedPayment',
      'SetPaymentBlock', 'ReleasePaymentBlock')
    AND "PayableItem_Changes"."Time" IS NOT NULL
